OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,FTennis fans were left disappointed
OL,7,Fafter British hopeful Jack Draper
OL,8,Ffollowed Emma Raducanu in dropping out
OL,9,Fof Wimbledon.
OL,11,FDraper revealed he has suffered a
OL,12,Frecurrence of an arm injury, after a
OL,13,Fdifficult year of tennis for the 24-
OL,14,Fyear-old from Sutton, which has seen
OL,15,Fhim play in only a handful of
OL,16,Ftournaments.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
