OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,FHis decision, on the tournament's
OL,7,Fopening day, came after British
OL,8,Fwomen's number one Raducanu withdrew
OL,9,Ffrom the competition on Sunday evening
OL,10,Fdue to a stress fracture in her lower
OL,11,Fright leg.Deborah Gamble, from Notting
OL,12,FHill, west London, said she would
OL,13,F"definitely" have tried to watch both
OL,14,FDraper and Raducanu and was sad to
OL,15,Fhear the news.
OL,17,FMs Gamble said "a lot of people were
OL,18,Flooking forward to watching both of
OL,19,Fthem", adding: "I, personally, am sad
OL,20,Fnot to watch them."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]yD@POU{D@EO]{D@POU|D@SO]
