PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782820091
OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,FTeaching assistant Martin Morrissey
OL,7,Fand school librarian Sol Elliott were
OL,8,Fequally disappointed to lose Draper
OL,9,Ffrom the grand slam.
OL,11,FMr Morrissey, from south London, said
OL,12,Fit was a shame the tournament will
OL,13,Ffeature few big-name British players
OL,14,Fthis year, describing Draper's exit
OL,15,Ffrom the tournament as "terrible" news.
OL,17,FHe said the pair had tickets for Court
OL,18,FOne and had been "looking forward" to
OL,19,Fseeing Raducanu, adding: "It would've
OL,20,Fbeen nice to have seen her play."
OL,26,@wD@XOUwD@aO]zD@ROUzD@bO]{D@ZOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
