CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782820091
OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,FDespite the bad news, the colleagues
OL,7,Fwere still enjoying soaking up the
OL,8,Fatmosphere of the tournament after
OL,9,Fwinning tickets through a ballot at
OL,10,FOverton Grange School, in Sutton,
OL,11,Fwhere they both work.
OL,13,FThe pair were also proud to see that
OL,14,Fpupils from the comprehensive state
OL,15,Fschool were serving as ball boys and
OL,16,Fball girls on the courts, adding it
OL,17,Fwas good to see the tournament's
OL,18,Finclusivity.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
