PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782820091
OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,FSteve Lewis, who travelled to
OL,7,FWimbledon from Swansea, South Wales,
OL,8,Falso had tickets for Court One and had
OL,9,Fbeen looking forward to watching
OL,10,FRaducanu.
OL,12,FInstead he saw Britain's Harriet Dart
OL,13,Fwho he said put up a good fight
OL,14,Fagainst Latvia's Jelena Ostapenko.
OL,16,FDespite her defeat, Mr Lewis said Dart
OL,17,Fmade fans proud, adding: "We were
OL,18,Fexpecting to see Emma but Harriet was
OL,19,Ffantastic... she really gave it her
OL,20,Fall.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
