CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782820091
OL,3,CWhy Jack Draper is not playing at
OL,4,CWimbledon 2026
OL,6,F"She was holding up the flag for GB,"
OL,7,Fhe added.
OL,9,FThere was more disappointment for
OL,10,FBritain when men's number one Cameron
OL,11,FNorrie, a former semi-finalist, was a
OL,12,Fshock first-round casualty when he was
OL,13,Fbeaten in a final-set tie-break by
OL,14,FAmerican qualifier Michael Zheng after
OL,15,Fa four-hour marathon on Court Two.
